column2: TINDAKMALAYSIA NETWORK SERVICES PLT (TINDAK MALAYSIA)

Election Commission of Malaysia (SPR), Tindak Malaysia (2021), PKR,Florczyk A.J., Corbane C., Ehrlich D., Freire S., Kemper T., Maffenini L., Melchiorri M., Pesaresi M., Politis P., Schiavina
M., Sabo F., Zanchetta L., GHSL Data Package 2019, EUR 29788 EN, Publications Office of the European Union, Luxembourg, 2019, ISBN
978-92-76-08725-0, doi:10.2760/062975, JRC 117104

All the percentages for electoral demographics are calculated by Tindak Malaysia. There is no official data for ethnic demographics and they are estimated by Tindak Malaysia. There could be calculation errors for Bumiputera Sabah and Sarawak population for DUN Sungai Udang. TindakMalaysia Network Services PLT is not responsible  for any errors or ommissions arising from the original data or its derivatives
